data.description: Back on the market at no fault of the seller! Welcome Home! This amazing 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is nestled in the highly desirable neighborhood of Timberland Place.  Several updates have been made to this home, including backyard privacy fence, screened in back porch, gorgeous landscaping, vinyl plank flooring throughout the home, fresh paint, granite counter tops, tile back splash, tiled Jacuzzi tub/shower and so much more! As you walk in you are welcomed with a large open space with a gas fireplace and open kitchen with eat in area and bar.  You will enjoy the fresh, updated kitchen with granite counters, tile back splash, and updated lighting. The secondary bedrooms are good sized with large closets. The hall bathroom has been updated with a Jacuzzi tub and tiled shower. The owners suit offers an attached bathroom with a large shower and double sinks, and walk in closet. Out the backdoor you will find a screened in back porch surrounded by beautiful landscaping. Timberland Place is conveniently located in the desirable Lexington 1 school district between I-26 and I-20. The neighborhood offers a community pool, sidewalks, gazebo, and playground.
